No. 278. Jose Dolores Marquez et al., Appellants, v. The Maxwell Land Grant Company. Appeal from the Supreme Court of the Territory of New Mexico. January 16, 1908. Dismissed with costs on motion of counsel for appellants. Mr. Frank W. Clancy and Mr. George P. Merrick for appellants. No appearance for appellee.
